.cs 4 on
.item 'SHOW SPIFILE Command' 'Added 06/24/85 by AEH'
.boxon
SHOW SPIFILE filename
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
The SHOW SPIFILE command displays whether an ORVYL file is
accessible only by SPIRES programs or by any ORVYL program.  The SET
SPIFILE command blocks access to an ORVYL file from any non-SPIRES
program, and the SET NOSPIFIL command reverses the SET SPIFIL
command.
.cs 4 off

